# lastTransactionsItem

**Object**

The most recent App Store-signed transaction information and App Store-signed renewal information for an auto-renewable subscription.

## Declaration

```swift
object lastTransactionsItem
```

## Data Types

- **originalTransactionId**: The original transaction identifier of a purchase.
- **status**: The status of an auto-renewable subscription.
- **JWSRenewalInfo**: Subscription renewal information, signed by the App Store, in JSON Web Signature (JWS) format.
- **JWSTransaction**: Transaction information signed by the App Store, in JSON Web Signature (JWS) Compact Serialization format.

## Object and Data Types
